y\" status\n- Verify messages exist in the specified date range\n\n## Development\n\n### Project Structure\n```\nsrc/\nâ”œâ”€â”€ index.js                 # Main entry point\nâ”œâ”€â”€ mcp-server.js           # MCP server implementation\nâ”œâ”€â”€ whatsapp-client.js      # WhatsApp client wrapper\nâ”œâ”€â”€ database.js             # SQLite database operations\nâ”œâ”€â”€ local-vector-store.js   # FAISS vector store\nâ”œâ”€â”€ message-processor.js    # Message processing logic\nâ””â”€â”€ config.js              # Configuration management\n```\n\n### Adding New Features\n1. Add new MCP tools in `mcp-server.js`\n2. Extend database schema in `database.js`\n3. Update message processing in `message-processor.js`\n4. Add vector search capabilities in `local-vector-store.js`\n\n## License\n\nMIT License",
